IMAPStore oniani-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User onianidavid@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass email"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore oniani-local
Subfolders Verbatim
PATH /home/oniani/.local/share/mail/
Inbox /home/oniani/.local/share/mail/INBOX

Channel oniani
Expunge Both
Far :oniani-remote:
Near :oniani-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"*fts-flatcurve*" !"*virtual*"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
